criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Curative and adjuvant radiotherapy for head and neck tumors;

          -  PS 1-2;

          -  Patient collaboration in evaluation of the toxicity diary.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Palliative radiotherapy in the head and neck tumor;

          -  PS 3;

          -  Non-compliance of the patient.
